WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.466 --> 00:00:08.766
What does Lu Chenyu mean?

2
00:00:08.766 --> 00:00:09.966
My parents finally got together

3
00:00:09.966 --> 00:00:11.066
Why are you here to make trouble?

4
00:00:11.066 --> 00:00:12.700
I'm not here to make trouble.

5
00:00:12.700 --> 00:00:15.233
I'm here to make amends, I don't need you to make amends

6
00:00:16.733 --> 00:00:18.900
Du Changyu, I want to divorce you

7
00:00:19.366 --> 00:00:20.633
I don't agree.

8
00:00:21.166 --> 00:00:23.066
I started a long time ago

9
00:00:23.066 --> 00:00:24.933
My dream is to marry you

10
00:00:24.933 --> 00:00:27.000
There's no way I'm going to let go.

11
00:00:28.100 --> 00:00:29.866
Don't you like Witt?

12
00:00:30.066 --> 00:00:32.666
But you are Witt, no

13
00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:35.300
I'm not Witt, just my disguise

14
00:00:35.533 --> 00:00:37.000
I'm still the same buckwheat I used to be

15
00:00:37.366 --> 00:00:39.000
The one you hate

16
00:00:40.733 --> 00:00:42.066
Do you really think

17
00:00:42.600 --> 00:00:44.366
I don't know who you really are.

18
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:49.266
What do you mean?

19
00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:53.000
You already knew that, what did you say?

20
00:00:54.300 --> 00:00:56.200
I just haven't exposed you, have I?

21
00:00:56.566 --> 00:00:57.700
I look at you and want to play

22
00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.966
Then I'll play with you

23
00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:03.833
Whether it's buckwheat or Witt

24
00:01:03.966 --> 00:01:05.000
It's all you

25
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:07.266
I like it as long as it's you.

26
00:01:07.300 --> 00:01:09.966
I want to be glib

27
00:01:10.333 --> 00:01:12.033
I don't like men like you the most

28
00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:14.333
But this man you hate the most?

29
00:01:14.333 --> 00:01:15.700
I like you the most.

